com.github.dandelion.core.bundle.loader.support

Class BowerPreLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.dandelion.core.bundle.loader.AbstractBundlePreLoader
      • com.github.dandelion.core.bundle.loader.support.BowerPreLoader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PreLoader

    public class BowerPreLoader
extends AbstractBundlePreLoader

    Extra loader intended to scan for Bower components and convert the Bower manifests into BundleStorageUnit.

    Note that bower.json files that do not contain a main parameter won't be loaded.

    Since:
    1.1.0
    Author:
    Thibault Duchateau
    See Also:
    DandelionConfig.BOWER_COMPONENTS_LOCATION

      • resolveLocationType

        public com.github.dandelion.core.bundle.loader.support.BowerPreLoader.LocationType resolveLocationType(String bowerComponentsLocation)

        Resolves the type of location of the bower_components directory using the prefix of the DandelionConfig.BOWER_COMPONENTS_LOCATION option.

        Always fallback to LocationType#webapp.

        Parameters:
        bowerComponentsLocation - The location of the bower_components set in the configuration option.
        Returns:
        the location type.
